Single oc Command to Apply LimitRange
bash
Copy
Edit
oc apply -f - <<EOF
apiVersion: v1
kind: LimitRange
metadata:
  name: pvc-default-500gi
  namespace: xyz
spec:
  limits:
  - type: PersistentVolumeClaim
    default:
      storage: 500Gi
    defaultRequest:
      storage: 500Gi
    max:
      storage: 500Gi
EOF
âœ… This does not require a file, and you can run it after namespace xyz is auto-created (e.g., during or just after your CDS install starts).

ðŸ§ª Optional Validation
bash
Copy
Edit
oc get limitrange -n xyz
oc describe limitrange pvc-default-500gi -n xyz
